						<summary>

						<p>On a sculptured slab fixed into the <hi rend="italic">gōpura</hi> of the Chennakēśavasvāmin temple.</p>						

						<p>Dated in Śaka 15[77], <hi rend="italic">Manmatha, Jyēshṭha,</hi> śu. 15 corresponding to A.D. 1655, June 8.</p>						

						<p>Seems to refer to Kandamūri Vīrapa, probably as the sculptor who made the image of Chennakēśava.</p>						

